column1: Baby Barnaby's////I'm a huge breakfast/brunch person so I get really excited when it comes to trying new spots. What stuck out to me was the influx of reviews about green eggs so I obviously had to make my way here. Who would've thought green eggs could taste so good?! This is the first time I've eaten at a restaurant and loved everything on my plate. There's usually one side item that doesn't wow me but this entire plate had me blown away. So yes
column2: my review is based on just one breakfast item and honestly
column3: I'm too obsessed to even try anything else.
